SIZE: Deluxe (7' Tall)
BEAST MODE: African Lion

LEO - A.K.A. Leo Jr - has grown up under the tutalage of Wingsaber and Santon.
Once a very rash and inexperienced robot who often ddidn't think things through 
he has grown into a wise and caring individual. He has a kind spark and only 
wants to view others as equals 

He can combine with Wingsaber and Santon to form Magnaboss II. 
